        <briefdescription>
<para>Retrieves the wakeup event info for an app that was launched by a wakeup_event (ie. <ref refid="group___launch_reason_1ga1674ca6a6f48cb98b8762da667eadfc1" kindref="member">launch_reason()</ref> === APP_LAUNCH_WAKEUP) so that an app may display information regarding the wakeup event. </para>
